Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是奧利弗•奎恩\N{\b0\fs12}My name is Oliver Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,五年裡  我被困在地獄一般的小島上\N{\b0\fs12}After five years on a hellish island,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來只有一個目標\N{\b0\fs12}I have come home with only one goal--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救我的城市\N{\b0\fs12}To save my city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但要達到目標  我不能像過去一樣成為兇手\N{\b0\fs12}But to do so, I can't be the killer I once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,為了紀念我的朋友  我只能偽裝成另一個人\N{\b0\fs12}To honor my friend's memory, I must be someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,成為另一個存在\N{\b0\fs12}I must be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,《綠箭》前情回顧\N{\b0\fs12}Previously on "Arrow"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}Slade!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一個有能力修船的人\N{\b0\fs12}I need someone qualified to fix this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.60,0:00:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望亨德里克先生跟你在一起\N{\b0\fs12}I sure hope a Mr. Hendrik is there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我死也不會回去的\N{\b0\fs12}There's no way in hell I'm going back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託  把槍放下\N{\b0\fs12}Please, put the gun down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在你瞭解什麼叫徹底絕望前  \N{\b0\fs12}You cannot die until you have known
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓你死的\N{\b0\fs12}complete despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你會瞭解的  我向你承諾\N{\b0\fs12}And you will, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,遠離西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Stay away from Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我做不到\N{\b0\fs12}No...I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她在你身邊的時候非常不安全  你愛她\N{\b0\fs12}She's not safe when she's around you. You love her,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你要按我說的做\N{\b0\fs12}and that's why you're going to do what I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這是個危險的城市\N{\b0\fs12}It's a dangerous city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:00:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,威爾遜先生\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Wilson?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:00:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我斯萊德就行\N{\b0\fs12}Call me Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.11,0:01:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你的睫毛膏花了\N{\b0\fs12}Your mascara is running.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧\N{\b0\fs12}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的男友\N{\b0\fs12}It's my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,現在是前男友了\N{\b0\fs12}Ex-boyfriend now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他突然決定和我分手\N{\b0\fs12}He just completely out of nowhere decides to end things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我太瞭解心碎這回事了\N{\b0\fs12}Heartbreak is something I know all too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦心碎很難恢復的\N{\b0\fs12}It's not an easy thing to recover from.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有時永遠都好不了\N{\b0\fs12}Sometimes you never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不是在...\N{\b0\fs12}Um, we're not at--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是我家\N{\b0\fs12}This isn't my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你不回家  西婭\N{\b0\fs12}You're not going home, Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,下車\N{\b0\fs12}Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,下車\N{\b0\fs12}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Hello, Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,見到你真高興\N{\b0\fs12}It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}星城哨兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沒時間了\N{\b0\fs12}No time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,今年  你放那些壞人一條生路\N{\b0\fs12}You letting the bad guys stay alive this year
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,後果就是監獄都已經滿員了\N{\b0\fs12}has filled the jails up to capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在和莎拉練習\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I've been working with Sara,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但我沒天賦\N{\b0\fs12}but I'm not exactly a natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我也沒有\N{\b0\fs12}Neither was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我們要忙活了\N{\b0\fs12}Ok. We have some work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我今天\N{\b0\fs12}Sorry, I'm just having a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很難專注於我們要幹的事\N{\b0\fs12}hard time keeping my head in the game today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因為西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Thea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想\N{\b0\fs12}I just can't stop thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我告訴她真相  最糟糕的後果會是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}what's the worst that can happen if I just told her the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我告訴了一個人真相  而他被閃電擊中了\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I told a guy the truth and he got struck by lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,說句公道話\N{\b0\fs12}To be fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,從統計學角度來看  也許不會再發生了\N{\b0\fs12}probably won't happen again, statistically.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴西婭真相不會讓她更安全\N{\b0\fs12}Telling Thea the truth won't make her safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,反而恰恰相反\N{\b0\fs12}Just the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  我們做的事很危險\N{\b0\fs12}What we're doing, Roy, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,任何在我們身邊的人都可能受傷\N{\b0\fs12}And anyone that is even in our orbit can get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,再試試\N{\b0\fs12}Try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這次\N{\b0\fs12}This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄準了\N{\b0\fs12}Aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,奎恩企業一個月的手機短信\N{\b0\fs12}About a month's worth of phone messages from Queen Consolidated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,扔了\N{\b0\fs12}Toss them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,上個月的手機短信我也扔了\N{\b0\fs12}That's what I did with last month's phone messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德還逍遙法外  我沒空管公司的事\N{\b0\fs12}With Slade out there, I don't have time for the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你得騰出時間  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Well, you have to make time, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,至少三小時\N{\b0\fs12}At least three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,年度董事會\N{\b0\fs12}The annual board meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,總裁不可能不出席的\N{\b0\fs12}There's absolutely zero way that the CEO can avoid being there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道有一陣子了\N{\b0\fs12}And I know it's been a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以別忘了  總裁是你\N{\b0\fs12}so in case you've forgotten, that's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你記得把西裝放哪兒了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you remember where you put your business suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,或者你把西裝也放在很酷的玻璃盒裡了\N{\b0\fs12}Or do you keep it in a cool glass case, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把你們都殺了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm going to kill all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是私人恩怨\N{\b0\fs12}This is not personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,也許有點吧\N{\b0\fs12}Well, maybe a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\b0\fs12}It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這是為了生存\N{\b0\fs12}This is about survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,生存  這樣說謀殺真好聽啊\N{\b0\fs12}Survival. What a noble word for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德讓我們別無選擇\N{\b0\fs12}Slade gave us no option.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,亨德里克換奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Hendrik for Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有什麼權力決定\N{\b0\fs12}And what gives any of us the right to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,誰的生命更有價值\N{\b0\fs12}one's life is more valuable than another?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他被綁起來了  我們沒有\N{\b0\fs12}He is tied up. We are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦他修好了船\N{\b0\fs12}Once he gets the boat working,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德就不需要他了\N{\b0\fs12}Slade will have no more need for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我們別自欺欺人了\N{\b0\fs12}So let's not kid ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣做就等於判了亨德里克的死刑\N{\b0\fs12}Doing this is effectively sentencing Hendrik to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,換做我們其中任何人  他也會這樣做的\N{\b0\fs12}He would do the same thing to any of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,毫不猶豫地這樣做\N{\b0\fs12}In heartbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這是唯一的選擇\N{\b0\fs12}This is only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果還有機會呢\N{\b0\fs12}What if it's also an opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼機會\N{\b0\fs12}To do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,殺斯萊德的機會\N{\b0\fs12}To kill Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我有一陣子沒來了\N{\b0\fs12}I know that I haven't been here in a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但你看起來不像是整個董事會成員吧\N{\b0\fs12}but you don't look like the entire board of directors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,會議半小時後才開始\N{\b0\fs12}The meeting doesn't start for another half hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我照例把所有預約的時間提前了30分鐘\N{\b0\fs12}I routinely bump all appointments 30 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,考慮到你經常遲到\N{\b0\fs12}in anticipation of you being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這辦法不錯\N{\b0\fs12}It's good policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但謝謝你為此不再冬眠了\N{\b0\fs12}But, thank you for coming out of hibernation for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你有沒有意識到  大樓上是你的名字\N{\b0\fs12}Whether you recognize it or not, it's your name on the building,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你缺席多少次會議\N{\b0\fs12}and no matter how many meetings you miss,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你依舊是公司的代言人\N{\b0\fs12}you're still the public face of this company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莎貝爾  我知道最近無暇顧及公司\N{\b0\fs12}Isabel, I realize I have been distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你幫我收拾爛攤子\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you for picking up the slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我們是非傳統的合夥人\N{\b0\fs12}Ours is an unconventional partnership,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但也是合夥人\N{\b0\fs12}but it's a partnership.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而且很有效\N{\b0\fs12}And it's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,的確是\N{\b0\fs12}Indeed it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你母親來了\N{\b0\fs12}Your mother's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,家庭矛盾嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Family squabble?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,羅切夫女士最近怎麼樣\N{\b0\fs12}And how is Ms. Rochev these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,還在因為自己家人的事生氣嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Still angry that Dorothy dropped a house on her sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你來幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-你跟西婭聯繫過嗎  -沒有\N{\b0\fs12}- Have you heard from Thea? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒有回我電話\N{\b0\fs12}You haven't returned any of my phone calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我沒有辦法只能當面找你\N{\b0\fs12}so I'm left to resort to checking in person
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,問你參不參加今晚的辯論會\N{\b0\fs12}as to whether you're attending the debate tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過我在公開場合會支援你競選的\N{\b0\fs12}I told you that I would publicly support your campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,還有事嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你今晚都不能有個好兒子的樣子\N{\b0\fs12}It would be embarrassing for us both
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們倆都會很尷尬的\N{\b0\fs12}if you couldn't at least appear to be my son tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我很擅長偽裝成別的樣子\N{\b0\fs12}I have gotten pretty good at pretending to be someone I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你學的\N{\b0\fs12}I learned it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了  你看見西婭•奎恩了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, excuse me, have you seen Thea Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,閃電妞  我是奧利  我在辯論會這裡\N{\b0\fs12}Speedy, it's Ollie, and I'm at the debate,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為你也在呢\N{\b0\fs12}where I thought you would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道羅伊的事你很生氣\N{\b0\fs12}Listen, I know that you're upset about Roy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但媽媽需要我們兩個都來\N{\b0\fs12}but mom needs both of us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以拜託了  回我電話\N{\b0\fs12}So please, just call me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起來不是很開心  一切還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You do not look happy. Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我的妹妹有點遲到了\N{\b0\fs12}Yes. My sister's just a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我想這可能是因為我\N{\b0\fs12}I'm afraid that's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,星城警局堅持車隊開到讓我過來\N{\b0\fs12}SCPD insisted that I arrive with a motorcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這阻礙了全市的交通\N{\b0\fs12}We tied up traffic all over the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭肯定是被堵在路上了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sure Thea's probably just fallen victim to gridlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我再給她打個電話試試\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I should probably try her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你今晚好運  塞巴斯蒂安\N{\b0\fs12}Good luck tonight, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為後臺是閒人勿進的\N{\b0\fs12}I thought backstage was supposed to be restricted access.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我想這就是做地區檢察官的好處吧\N{\b0\fs12}The benefits of having a district attorney's badge, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你來祝莫伊拉好運嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You stop by to wish Moira good luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  但我很高興碰到了你\N{\b0\fs12}I did. But I'm really glad I ran into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我應該向你道歉\N{\b0\fs12}I owe you an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾指責你做了很多糟糕的事\N{\b0\fs12}I accused you of really terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你當時正處在一個非常艱難的時期\N{\b0\fs12}You were going through a very difficult time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高興你慢慢恢復了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm just happy you're on the mend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你今晚好運\N{\b0\fs12}Good luck tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚需要運氣的可不是我\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not the one who's going to need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安•布拉德不是你們想的那樣\N{\b0\fs12}Sebastian Blood is not the man you think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他不會通過社會服務使城市復興\N{\b0\fs12}He's not going to revive the city with social services.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}星城市長競選辯論\N2014年度競選
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有資金支持的委任會讓城市破產\N{\b0\fs12}He's going to bankrupt it with unfunded mandates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,奎恩女士對我競選的不滿是\N{\b0\fs12}Mrs. Queen's problem with my proposals
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這一切都由那1%的富人買單\N{\b0\fs12}is that they will be paid for by the one percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是時候讓富人們\N{\b0\fs12}It's time that the wealthiest
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,擔起自己的責任了\N{\b0\fs12}people stop avoiding their responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但這會限制他們選人用人的能力\N{\b0\fs12}But it will limit their abilities to hire people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  時間到  我提醒候選人\N{\b0\fs12}All right, that's time, and I will remind the candidates
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要再打斷對方\N{\b0\fs12}to please refrain from interrupting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是下一位星城選民\N{\b0\fs12}Now we have the next in our series of video questions
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,通過視頻提出的問題\N{\b0\fs12}submitted by Starling City voters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,來自...西婭•奎恩\N{\b0\fs12}This one comes from... Thea Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是出錯了\N{\b0\fs12}Ok, there must be some mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\b0\fs12}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,救命  來人救救我  拜託\N{\b0\fs12}Help! Somebody help me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他  斯萊...\N{\b0\fs12}He--sla--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}西婭•奎恩的生命對你來說值多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會找到她的  羅伊  我們會救她回來的\N{\b0\fs12}We're going to find her, Roy. We're going to get her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她是個堅強的女孩\N{\b0\fs12}She's a tough girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我們找到她的時候她還會活著嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is she going to be alive when we find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能這麼想\N{\b0\fs12}You can't think like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒辦法不這麼想\N{\b0\fs12}I can't stop thinking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格爾先生\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Diggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格爾先生\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Diggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像有發現  正在查\N{\b0\fs12}I think I might have found something. I'm working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我暫停競選  貢獻一切資源\N{\b0\fs12}I am suspending my campaign and devoting its resources
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}西婭•奎恩遭綁架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,希望西婭•奎恩能安全回來\N{\b0\fs12}to the safe return of Thea Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,今天  是我們...\N{\b0\fs12}Today, the day we both...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,視頻上提到了要求  但沒提到贖金\N{\b0\fs12}Well, the video referenced a demand, but no ransom,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說這可能不是錢的事\N{\b0\fs12}which means this might not be about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會救她回來的  莫伊拉\N{\b0\fs12}We're going to get her back, Moira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保證  西婭會回家的\N{\b0\fs12}I promise you. Thea's coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你想想有沒有人\N{\b0\fs12}Now, can you think of anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,會想通過西婭來威脅你\N{\b0\fs12}who might want to get to you through Thea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,去年死去的那503個人的家屬都有可能\N{\b0\fs12}No one except for the families of the 503 people that died last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這跟地震沒有關係\N{\b0\fs12}This isn't about the quake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼能確定\N{\b0\fs12}Well, how can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你們只需要找到那個戴面具的人\N{\b0\fs12}You just need to find the man in the mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在找\N{\b0\fs12}Look, we're working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在追蹤每一條線索\N{\b0\fs12}We're running down every lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼線索\N{\b0\fs12}What are those leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  我怎麼會讓這種事發生\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, God, how could I have let this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,失陪一下\N{\b0\fs12}Excuse me for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果再讓我知道有一個\N{\b0\fs12}If I hear about one more
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有攻擊性的媒體調查傳送到奎恩先生\N{\b0\fs12}invasive press inquiry being sent to Mr. Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,或者奎恩家的任何家庭成員面前\N{\b0\fs12}or to any member of the Queen family,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我就唯你是問\N{\b0\fs12}I will hold you personally responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你這樣很嚇人啊  謝謝你\N{\b0\fs12}You're very scary. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我的工作是幫你處理事務  今天尤甚\N{\b0\fs12}My job is to take things off your plate, now more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,說到這個  你還記得在今天董事會上\N{\b0\fs12}To that end, you remember how at today's meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,董事成員提名的新管理人員嗎\N{\b0\fs12}the board nominated new officers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,投票需要在24小時之內進行\N{\b0\fs12}Voting has to take place within 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,美國證監會在看著呢  不能耽擱\N{\b0\fs12}It cannot be suspended. It's an SEC thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在沒心思想這個\N{\b0\fs12}I can't think about this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白  我很遺憾  但是你必須要想\N{\b0\fs12}I know, and I'm sorry, but you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你是公司的總裁  你有責任...\N{\b0\fs12}You're the CEO and you have responsibilities--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是你替我負責的\N{\b0\fs12}Which you handle for me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,董事會投票與替你出席會議\N{\b0\fs12}A board vote is several orders of magnitude, different
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是完全不同的\N{\b0\fs12}from covering a missed meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以臨時任命一位總裁\N{\b0\fs12}You could appoint someone CEO pro tempore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不過那不是個好主意\N{\b0\fs12}That's not a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在就任命你\N{\b0\fs12}I'm appointing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你\N{\b0\fs12}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在是臨時總裁\N{\b0\fs12}You are the temporary CEO.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\b0\fs12}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:10:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\b0\fs12}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,等西婭安全回家了  讓她謝謝我\N{\b0\fs12}Have Thea thank me, when she's back safe at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,奎恩先生  我需要和你談談威爾遜的事\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Queen? I need to talk to you, it's about Mr. Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭最後被看見是在威登酒吧\N{\b0\fs12}Since the last place Thea was seen was Verdant,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我通過信用卡記錄列出了昨晚客人的名單\N{\b0\fs12}I used credit card receipts, compiled a list of customers last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,追蹤了他們的電話  黑進去看了他們的照片\N{\b0\fs12}pinged all their cell phones and hacked into their photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,美國國家安全局是對的\N{\b0\fs12}The NSA is right;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不用申請批準確實方便多了\N{\b0\fs12}it's a lot easier when you don't need a warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我瀏覽了所有照片\N{\b0\fs12}I eyeballed every photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那得有幾千張照片\N{\b0\fs12}There must have been thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,為了西婭  我找到了這個\N{\b0\fs12}It's Thea. I found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在離酒吧三個街區處發現的部分車牌\N{\b0\fs12}Partial plate three blocks from the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,車子是在斯萊德•威爾遜名下的\N{\b0\fs12}Car's registered to a Slade Wilson,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,車裡有定位導航系統\N{\b0\fs12}and it has GPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,現在車在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Where is it right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,停在羅斯福街的一間倒閉的酒吧外\N{\b0\fs12}Parked outside a defunct bar on Roosevelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不覺得這樣太容易了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Ok, this doesn't seem easy to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德在自己的名下注冊了一輛車\N{\b0\fs12}Slade using a car registered in his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,整件事都很詭異\N{\b0\fs12}The whole thing smells rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,無論是西婭還是他在那裡\N{\b0\fs12}Either Thea's there or he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都得去看看\N{\b0\fs12}Either way, we have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你會這麼說\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, I figured you'd say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我已經提煉好了這個\N{\b0\fs12}which is why I worked up these.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,西藏蝮蛇毒\N{\b0\fs12}Tibetan pit viper venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,刺客聯盟的人一直用它\N{\b0\fs12}The league of assassins' poison of choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是我用過的最有效的鎮定劑\N{\b0\fs12}And the most powerful sedative that I've ever worked with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那會給我們帶來優勢\N{\b0\fs12}That'll give us an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,而你是我們的另一個優勢\N{\b0\fs12}But you are going to give us another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定要我跟著去嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you sure you want me to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你憤怒嗎  利用你的憤怒吧\N{\b0\fs12}Are you angry? Use that rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都讓我隱忍行事\N{\b0\fs12}Well, you're just always telling me to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚不用\N{\b0\fs12}Not tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,炸彈嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Landmines?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這個島是個什麼地方啊\N{\b0\fs12}What kind of island is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你會拆彈嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can you remove the explosive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,當然會\N{\b0\fs12}Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能在不引爆的情況下拆除\N{\b0\fs12}Without it going off, eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.47,0:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就不那麼確定了\N{\b0\fs12}Less certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,克格勃  我在那學到很多很多東西\N{\b0\fs12}Ah, KGB. You taught me many, many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,無論俄國炸彈\N{\b0\fs12}Russian bomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,還是日本炸彈\N{\b0\fs12}Japanese bomb;
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,它們都會...嘭\N{\b0\fs12}they both go...boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜  我們還活著  現在要怎麼做\N{\b0\fs12}Congratulations, we are not dead. Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我們按照約定讓斯萊德帶走亨德里克\N{\b0\fs12}Well, Slade takes Hendrik as we agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,等他們走得夠遠的時候...\N{\b0\fs12}And then once they're far enough away...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼\N{\b0\fs12}What--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你想把炸彈放到亨德里克身上\N{\b0\fs12}You want to rig Hendrik into bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得說得沒錯  把亨德里克交給斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}Well, Peter was right. Handing Hendrik over to Slade
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就等於殺了他  你說得也沒錯\N{\b0\fs12}is the same thing as killing him. And you're right, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我們別無選擇  不過  這樣至少\N{\b0\fs12}We don't have a choice. I mean, at least this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可以把斯萊德除掉\N{\b0\fs12}he can take out Slade,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣我們就可以登船了\N{\b0\fs12}and then we can take the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,只是  好奇\N{\b0\fs12}Just...wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼時候變得如此可怕了\N{\b0\fs12}When did you become so scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪裡  斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}Where is she, Slade?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他在問你問題\N{\b0\fs12}The man asked you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你要把我怎麼樣  小子  殺了我嗎\N{\b0\fs12}What are you going to do, kid? Kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的話誰會告訴你\N{\b0\fs12}But then who would tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你親愛的妹妹在什麼地方\N{\b0\fs12}where your beloved Thea is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,打電話給蘭斯警探\N{\b0\fs12}Call detective Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他來這裡\N{\b0\fs12}Tell him to come down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼  為什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Wh--what? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,來逮捕斯萊德•威爾遜\N{\b0\fs12}To arrest Slade Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道這個混蛋為什麼抓西婭•奎恩嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Any idea what this son of a bitch wants with Thea Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道  我們只需要\N{\b0\fs12}No. We just need to make
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,讓斯萊德說出他把西婭關在哪裡就行\N{\b0\fs12}sure that Slade gives up where he's holding her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗知道嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Does Oliver know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事是你跟綠箭一起行動的\N{\b0\fs12}That you're working with the Arrow on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,綠箭的事奧利弗什麼都不知道\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver doesn't know anything about the Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事  就是莫伊拉現在的眼神\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. It's just that look in Moira's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕已經失去女兒的那種眼神\N{\b0\fs12}terrified she's lost her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那種感覺我無法承受第二次了  莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}I couldn't go through that again, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,蘭斯警官\N{\b0\fs12}Officer Lance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,奎恩家的人到了\N{\b0\fs12}The Queen family's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,蘭斯先生  他告訴你西婭在哪了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Lance, did he tell you where Thea is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,奎恩夫人  謝謝你過來\N{\b0\fs12}Mrs. Queen, thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這實在是講不通\N{\b0\fs12}This doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德•威爾遜是我們的朋友\N{\b0\fs12}Slade Wilson is a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他過去的72小時都在哥斯達黎加\N{\b0\fs12}And he's been in Costa Rica for the past 72 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他有乘客名單證明  通話記錄\N{\b0\fs12}He can provide flight manifests, phone records,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至還有錄影證明\N{\b0\fs12}even some videos,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不可能是他抓了您女兒\N{\b0\fs12}so he couldn't have taken your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是他  為什麼要把他抓來 \N{\b0\fs12}If he didn't, then why did you arrest him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我們抓的  是治安維持者把他抓住的\N{\b0\fs12}We didn't. He was apprehended by the vigilante.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,然後聯繫了蘭斯警官\N{\b0\fs12}Who then contacted officer Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,局長  我可以解釋...\N{\b0\fs12}Lieutenant, I can explain--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我想我很清楚是怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}No, I think I got a pretty clear picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  你可真不是一般的笨\N{\b0\fs12}God, you're a special kind of stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你不戴警徽而穿那套制服的\N{\b0\fs12}The whole reason you're wearing that uniform
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一原因\N{\b0\fs12}instead of a detective's shield
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為你跟治安維持者同流合污了\N{\b0\fs12}is 'cause you were working with the vigilante.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一個小女孩失蹤了  你只是\N{\b0\fs12}A young girl is missing, and you just--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你就因為他一聲令下而逮捕了某人嗎\N{\b0\fs12}And now you arrest someone on his say-so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你下一個穿的制服\N{\b0\fs12}You'll be lucky if the next uniform
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不是囚服  你就慶幸吧\N{\b0\fs12}that puts you in isn't prison gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他們都叫你喪鐘\N{\b0\fs12}They're calling you Deathstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,有點兒太高調了\N{\b0\fs12}It's a bit flamboyant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜歡\N{\b0\fs12}I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼從島上逃出來的\N{\b0\fs12}How did you get off the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你問我的第一個問題嗎\N{\b0\fs12}That is your first question?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經表明\N{\b0\fs12}Well, you've made it pretty clear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不會告訴我妹妹的下落\N{\b0\fs12}that you're not going to tell me where my sister is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以沒錯  這是我問你的第一個問題\N{\b0\fs12}so, yeah. That's my first question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我遊出來的\N{\b0\fs12}I swam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但那也是經歷了千辛萬苦的\N{\b0\fs12}But it wasn't without its obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,激流想把我淹沒\N{\b0\fs12}The rip current dragged me under.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,暗礁上的石頭讓我皮開肉綻\N{\b0\fs12}The rocks on the reef cut up my flesh to the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是米拉庫魯\N{\b0\fs12}But the Mirakuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,讓一切都再生了\N{\b0\fs12}It regenerated everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,除了這隻眼\N{\b0\fs12}Except this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這房間裡只有我們兩個人\N{\b0\fs12}You know, it's just the two of us in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你說實話吧\N{\b0\fs12}so why don't we try being honest?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要這麼做\N{\b0\fs12}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道為什麼\N{\b0\fs12}You know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那是五年前的事了\N{\b0\fs12}It was five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,猶如昨天\N{\b0\fs12}It was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我試著想放開島上的事\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, I tried to let go of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但記憶依舊纏著我\N{\b0\fs12}but it's still got a hold on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你每晚都穿的兜帽是某種象徵的話\N{\b0\fs12}And if that hood that you wear every night is any indication,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,記憶也還纏著你啊  孩子\N{\b0\fs12}it's still got a hold of you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她對你什麼都沒做  是我做的\N{\b0\fs12}She never did anything to you. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,莎朵是因為我所做的選擇而死\N{\b0\fs12}Shado is dead because of a choice that I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以懲罰我  責怪我\N{\b0\fs12}So punish me. Blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\b0\fs12}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你想讓我求你嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You want me to beg?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你的目的嗎  讓我求你\N{\b0\fs12}Is that what this all about? Because I'm begging.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你贏了\N{\b0\fs12}You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\b0\fs12}Just, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,請告訴我她在哪兒\N{\b0\fs12}Please tell me where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你能這樣說一定很不容易\N{\b0\fs12}Hmm, that must have been hard for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Thea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭在...\N{\b0\fs12}Well, Thea's--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,奎恩先生\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,誰讓你進來的\N{\b0\fs12}Who the hell let you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,威爾遜先生\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Wilson...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以走了\N{\b0\fs12}you are free to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,警局深深地向你道歉\N{\b0\fs12}with the department's deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  警督\N{\b0\fs12}There's no need, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一名無辜的女孩生死未卜\N{\b0\fs12}An innocent girl's life hangs in the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要追查一切有希望的線索\N{\b0\fs12}You need to follow every lead possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但你還是應該知道蘭斯警官\N{\b0\fs12}Well, still, you should know that Officer Lance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,會面對很嚴重的罪行指控\N{\b0\fs12}is facing some very serious charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,別以我的名義起訴他們\N{\b0\fs12}Well, don't pursue them on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不是會記仇的人\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not one to hold a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,威爾遜先生  威爾遜先生\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Wilson, Mr. Wilson,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,警方已經撤銷對你的所有指控了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}have the police cleared you of all charges?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我當時在哥斯達黎加  但一聽到這個噩耗\N{\b0\fs12}I was in Costa Rica, but returned to Starling City
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就立刻回到了星城\N{\b0\fs12}as soon as I heard the terrible news.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,關於奎恩的失蹤  你是怎麼跟他們說的\N{\b0\fs12}What did you tell them about Thea Queen's disappearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我向他們提供了我所能支配的一切資源\N{\b0\fs12}I'm offering every resource at my disposal,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,再加上五百萬美元懸賞\N{\b0\fs12}plus a $5 million reward
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,以求任何關於綁架西婭•奎恩的人的信息\N{\b0\fs12}for any information that leads to Thea Queen's captors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我是狄格  我正跟著他 \N{\b0\fs12}This is Dig, I've got the follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在他車上安的追蹤器運轉正常\N{\b0\fs12}Tracker on his car is active.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  他正往你那邊走去\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, he's coming up on your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看到他了  他拐入了沃納街 \N{\b0\fs12}Got him. He's turning up Warner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了  正往北方走\N{\b0\fs12}I see him. Heading north.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,該死  我跟丟了\N{\b0\fs12}Damn it, I lost him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事  我還跟著他\N{\b0\fs12}It's all right. I still have eyes on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉  右轉去唐尼街\N{\b0\fs12}Sara, cut right onto Downey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\b0\fs12}Got 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不是  不是  不是他的車\N{\b0\fs12}Negative. Negative, it's not him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他克隆了追蹤器的信號\N{\b0\fs12}He's cloned the tracker's signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  你得趕快移動\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, you've got to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  你得在福勒街上追蹤到他\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, you got to pick him up on Fuller.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  你還跟著他嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, do you still have eyes on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}Roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}Roy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,出去\N{\b0\fs12}Leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起我離開了這麼久\N{\b0\fs12}Sorry I was gone for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧\N{\b0\fs12}Screw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我看見奧利弗和你母親了\N{\b0\fs12}I saw Oliver and your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他們都非常擔心你\N{\b0\fs12}They're all quite worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你敢傷害他們  我發誓我要...\N{\b0\fs12}If you hurt them, I swear I--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,請繼續說\N{\b0\fs12}Please. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,把那句子說完\N{\b0\fs12}Finish that sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好奇一個十九歲的女孩\N{\b0\fs12}I'm curious to know what kind of threat
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,能做出什麼樣的威脅\N{\b0\fs12}a 19-year-old girl can make.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要我怎麼樣\N{\b0\fs12}What do you want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛  西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Well, that, Thea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,說來話長\N{\b0\fs12}is a very long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看來我有的是時間\N{\b0\fs12}Looks like I've got time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,並沒有\N{\b0\fs12}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以走了\N{\b0\fs12}You're free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要表明一個觀點\N{\b0\fs12}I had to make a point,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我表明了\N{\b0\fs12}and I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,門沒鎖\N{\b0\fs12}The door is unlocked,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼時候想離開都可以\N{\b0\fs12}so you can leave any time you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但那些為你工作的人\N{\b0\fs12}But those guys who work for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我一走出去就會朝我開槍\N{\b0\fs12}will shoot me the second I walk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不會的\N{\b0\fs12}No, they won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他們的任務只是在我回來之前看住你\N{\b0\fs12}Their instructions were to keep you here until I returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.28,0:21:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我已經回來了  所以\N{\b0\fs12}And I have. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以離開了\N{\b0\fs12}you're free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但一旦你走了\N{\b0\fs12}But, if you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就永遠不會知道你哥哥的秘密了\N{\b0\fs12}you may never know about your brother's secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥哥有一個秘密  西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Your brother has a secret, Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,想知道是什麼嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Would you like to know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\b0\fs12}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,現在該怎麼做\N{\b0\fs12}what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Wait for Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,想想下一步該怎麼做\N{\b0\fs12}Figure out what our next move will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說等他的命令吧\N{\b0\fs12}Wait for him to tell us, you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:21:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有奎恩國王的聖旨我們什麼也不能做\N{\b0\fs12}We can't do anything without King Queen's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:21:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你話說過頭了  羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}You're out of line, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  大家都冷靜一下\N{\b0\fs12}All right, let's all just calm down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德暫占上風  這是兵家常事\N{\b0\fs12}Slade outplayed us. It happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.61,0:22:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不  都怪員警放走了斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}No, it only happened because the police let Slade go--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.29,0:22:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,而那是奧利弗叫我們把他送進去的\N{\b0\fs12}after we turned him in, because Oliver told us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我們該怎麼做呢\N{\b0\fs12}What were we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你是特種部隊的\N{\b0\fs12}You're Special Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她是個跨國殺手\N{\b0\fs12}She's an international assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,憑我們三個  \N{\b0\fs12}You would think between the three of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不把他交給員警\N{\b0\fs12}we could have gotten answers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也就逼出答案了\N{\b0\fs12}out of Slade ourselves instead of turning him into the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,最噁心的是  他說要這麼做\N{\b0\fs12}Here's what's really sick; is we didn't even question him
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都沒有人質疑是不是應該如此\N{\b0\fs12}because he said it was the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就像他說我該和西婭分手\N{\b0\fs12}Just like he said that I needed to break up with Thea
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,而一周之前\N{\b0\fs12}one week after telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他還告訴我讓西婭一個人不安全\N{\b0\fs12}that it wasn't safe for me to leave her alone--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\b0\fs12}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.42,0:22:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你覺得斯萊德抓走西婭是奧利弗的錯\N{\b0\fs12}You think it's oliver's fault that Slade took Thea?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我認為我沒能阻止斯萊德是他的錯\N{\b0\fs12}I think it was his fault that I wasn't there to stop Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我認為你只是因為跟丟了斯萊德而遷怒於他\N{\b0\fs12}And I think you're just blaming Oliver because you lost Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你們正搞在一起  你當然幫他說話了\N{\b0\fs12}Well, of course you'd take his side, you're screwing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.86,0:22:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,能讓我們單獨待一會嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can you guys give us a minute, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你記不記得她多愛畫畫\N{\b0\fs12}Do you remember how she loved to color?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸一箱一箱地給她買蠟筆\N{\b0\fs12}Your father would buy her boxes of crayons by the truckload.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,卻總是滿足不了她\N{\b0\fs12}She could never get enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.44,0:23:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她老在牆上畫畫\N{\b0\fs12}She'd draw on the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我卻總生不起氣來  因為她如此可愛\N{\b0\fs12}And I could never get angry, because it was just so adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.45,0:23:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該去休息一下\N{\b0\fs12}You should try to get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我的寶貝還活著嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is my baby still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.78,0:23:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我的寶貝還活著嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is my baby still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.70,0:23:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.06,0:23:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍受了喪子之痛整整五年\N{\b0\fs12}I woke up every day for five years the mother who lost her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,0:23:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\b0\fs12}I-- I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能再承受一次了\N{\b0\fs12}I can't endure it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你對我恨之入骨\N{\b0\fs12}And now you hate me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.28,0:24:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而且並非是無理取鬧\N{\b0\fs12}and you have every justification.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-現在不合適  -就是現在\N{\b0\fs12}- Now is not the time. - Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.37,0:24:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這是最好的時機\N{\b0\fs12}It is exactly the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.88,0:24:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我告訴過你那些欺騙\N{\b0\fs12}I've told you that these lies
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.15,0:24:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是為了保護家人\N{\b0\fs12}were to keep our family safe;
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們團結\N{\b0\fs12}to keep us all together,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.33,0:24:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但那就是最大的謊言\N{\b0\fs12}but that was the biggest lie of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.43,0:24:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我用它欺騙了你  西婭\N{\b0\fs12}And I told it to you, to Thea,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.22,0:24:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,和我自己\N{\b0\fs12}to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.19,0:24:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我太脆弱\N{\b0\fs12}Because I was too weak
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.48,0:24:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不能面對真相\N{\b0\fs12}to face any kind of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.95,0:24:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,現在發生的事不是你的錯\N{\b0\fs12}What's happening now isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.96,0:24:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,從子女出生起\N{\b0\fs12}From the moment your children are born,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.07,0:24:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你就擔心世界會不會傷害他們\N{\b0\fs12}you worry what the world might do to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.27,0:25:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但你最擔心的是自己會不會傷害他們\N{\b0\fs12}But you never stop to think what you might do to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.69,0:25:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可能就是自己最大的敵人\N{\b0\fs12}That we could be our own worst enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.81,0:25:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利\N{\b0\fs12}Ollie!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.01,0:25:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你對他做了什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What did you do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.44,0:25:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不足掛齒\N{\b0\fs12}Not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.74,0:25:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你又對他做了什麼\N{\b0\fs12}And what did you do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.22,0:25:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我們把他打暈了  這樣比較方便\N{\b0\fs12}We just knocked him. It's better that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.55,0:25:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他不太贊成這場交易\N{\b0\fs12}He wasn't exactly a fan of the arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.32,0:25:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可想而知\N{\b0\fs12}I would imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.63,0:25:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,亨德里克是你的了\N{\b0\fs12}Hendrik's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.30,0:25:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\b0\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.58,0:26:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\b0\fs12}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.40,0:26:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,米拉庫魯真個很神奇的東西\N{\b0\fs12}It's an incredible thing, this Mirakuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.23,0:26:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,它不僅給了我力量\N{\b0\fs12}Not only does it give you strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.27,0:26:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,還強化了我的感官\N{\b0\fs12}it also heightens all of your senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.00,0:26:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,炸藥有一種特殊的味道\N{\b0\fs12}TNT has a particular smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.65,0:26:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還有多久爆炸\N{\b0\fs12}How long before it goes off?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.52,0:26:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,90秒\N{\b0\fs12}90 seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.47,0:26:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,還是60秒\N{\b0\fs12}60 seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.00,0:26:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你們可能以為爆炸能殺死我\N{\b0\fs12}You're probably thinking that the blast would kill me,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.14,0:26:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不這麼認為\N{\b0\fs12}but I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.52,0:26:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你們就不一樣了\N{\b0\fs12}Not that I could say the same for you lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.93,0:26:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我迫不及待\N{\b0\fs12}I am tempted
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.80,0:26:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,想看到你被炸成碎片\N{\b0\fs12}to see this blow you to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.06,0:26:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不過話說回來  也許我可以直接殺死你\N{\b0\fs12}But then again, maybe I'll just shoot you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.78,0:26:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就像他殺死莎朵一樣\N{\b0\fs12}the same way that he shot Shado.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.07,0:26:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.65,0:27:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}Slade...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.08,0:27:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.47,0:27:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,乾坐在這裡可幫不了西婭  不是嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Well, sitting around here isn't helping Thea, now is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.47,0:27:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你這樣魯莽行事是不行的 羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}Neither is you running off half-cocked, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.89,0:27:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你們認為\N{\b0\fs12}I know that you think
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.70,0:27:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是米拉庫魯在影響我  但並非如此\N{\b0\fs12}that this is the Mirakuru, but it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.60,0:27:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我是對的  你也清楚\N{\b0\fs12}I'm right, and you know that I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.55,0:27:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你最好別他媽擋著我\N{\b0\fs12}So you better get the hell out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.07,0:27:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  冷靜點\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.49,0:27:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭也會希望我們這麼做的\N{\b0\fs12}It's what Thea would want us to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.98,0:27:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她說的對  羅伊  我們先按兵不動\N{\b0\fs12}She's right, Roy. Come on, let's throttle back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.16,0:27:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,下一箭會直穿你的心臟\N{\b0\fs12}Next one goes into your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.55,0:27:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,放開他\N{\b0\fs12}Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.77,0:27:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的要因為\N{\b0\fs12}You would honestly kill me because I dare
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.64,0:27:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我批評全能的奧利弗•奎恩而殺我嗎\N{\b0\fs12}to criticize the almighty Oliver Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.66,0:27:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我殺你是因為你正在傷害我的朋友\N{\b0\fs12}No, I'd kill you because you're hurting my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.45,0:27:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,放開他\N{\b0\fs12}Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.54,0:27:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,放開他\N{\b0\fs12}Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.05,0:27:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這下面到底怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}What the hell's going on down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.90,0:27:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不幹了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.99,0:27:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}That's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.44,0:28:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭在外頭受傷了或是更糟  因為一個人\N{\b0\fs12}Thea, she's out there, hurt or worse, because of one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.34,0:28:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而那個人不是斯萊德•威爾遜\N{\b0\fs12}And that is not Slade Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.37,0:28:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}Roy...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.49,0:28:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾那麼信任你\N{\b0\fs12}I believed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.17,0:28:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經沒有理由留下了\N{\b0\fs12}There's nothing left for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.23,0:28:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-我的天  奧利弗  -又怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}- Oh, my god. Oliver... - Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.67,0:28:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,宣傳部起草了一份很有力的聲明\N{\b0\fs12}Publicity has drafted a rather compelling statement,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.92,0:28:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我會去參加脫口秀來引導輿論導向\N{\b0\fs12}and I will be doing the talk show rounds to control the spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.94,0:28:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  羅切夫女士  但他很\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry, Ms. Rochev, but he was very...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.12,0:28:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,急迫\N{\b0\fs12}insistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.75,0:28:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你們先出去吧\N{\b0\fs12}Can you give us the room, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.61,0:28:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莎貝爾  你幹了什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Isabel, what have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.96,0:28:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我嗎  沒做什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Me? Very little.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.75,0:28:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你讓我當上總裁之時\N{\b0\fs12}You're the one who made this possible
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.07,0:28:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就讓這一切有了可能\N{\b0\fs12}when you made me CEO.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.28,0:28:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道只是暫時的\N{\b0\fs12}I know it was only temporary,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.55,0:28:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但給了我所需要的權限\N{\b0\fs12}but it gave me the authority I needed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.88,0:29:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,來召集緊急董事會\N{\b0\fs12}to call an emergency board meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.00,0:29:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就在半小時前\N{\b0\fs12}As of 30 minutes ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.07,0:29:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你的公司歸我了\N{\b0\fs12}your company belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.98,0:29:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,董事們一致同意將我的任命變成永久性的\N{\b0\fs12}The directors unanimously made my appointment permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.75,0:29:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來想說他們對你的領導力失去了信任\N{\b0\fs12}I'd say they lost faith in your leadership,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.13,0:29:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不過那樣聽起來就好像你有領導力似的\N{\b0\fs12}but that would imply there was any.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.77,0:29:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也許你應該少花點精力在你的\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe you should have focused a little less on your...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.03,0:29:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,晚間活動上\N{\b0\fs12}evening activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.32,0:29:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}Slade...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.15,0:29:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你為他工作\N{\b0\fs12}You're working for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.78,0:29:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,和他工作\N{\b0\fs12}With.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.75,0:29:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道把我安插進你的家族企業\N{\b0\fs12}He knew planting me in your family's business
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.55,0:29:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,會把你拉回星城\N{\b0\fs12}would draw you back to Starling City.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.18,0:29:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,說實話  我很懷疑  但是\N{\b0\fs12}Truth be told, I was skeptical, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.61,0:29:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你要這麼做\N{\b0\fs12}Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.52,0:29:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道還真是可悲\N{\b0\fs12}I think it's sad you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.27,0:29:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,父債子還\N{\b0\fs12}The sins of the father are the sins of the son.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.26,0:30:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快告訴我  我妹妹在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}You are going to tell me where my sister is,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.55,0:30:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,否則我就殺了你\N{\b0\fs12}or I am going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.99,0:30:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪兒\N{\b0\fs12}Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.20,0:30:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他把她關在一個貨站裡\N{\b0\fs12}He's holding her at a storage depot
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.91,0:30:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就在市區邊上  托斯卡貨運\N{\b0\fs12}just outside the city limits. Tosca Cartage.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.17,0:30:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼知道你不是在騙我\N{\b0\fs12}How do I know you're not lying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.84,0:30:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你真可愛  你還不知道吧\N{\b0\fs12}It's cute how you think this isn't all playing out
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.10,0:30:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,事情進展正像他所希望的那樣\N{\b0\fs12}exactly how he wants it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.64,0:30:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他希望你一個人去\N{\b0\fs12}And he wants you to come alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.55,0:30:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他嗅到了你搭檔的氣息\N{\b0\fs12}If he even smells your partners,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.31,0:30:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他會把小西婭像條鮭魚一樣開膛破肚\N{\b0\fs12}he will gut sweet little Thea like a trout.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.99,0:30:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你共事很愉快  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}It was a pleasure doing business with you, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.23,0:30:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,至少讓我們包圍周邊地區\N{\b0\fs12}At least let us surround the perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.74,0:30:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不  伊莎貝爾說的很明白\N{\b0\fs12}No, Isabel was very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.16,0:30:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我一個人去  否則西婭性命難保\N{\b0\fs12}I come alone or Thea dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.68,0:30:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利  這是斯萊德的又一個遊戲  除非\N{\b0\fs12}Ollie, this is another one of Slade's games, and unless--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.28,0:30:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我什麼都做不了  莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}No, what I can't do, Sara, is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.78,0:30:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是勞蕾爾你會怎麼做\N{\b0\fs12}What would you do if it were Laurel,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.27,0:30:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是你的父親或者母親呢\N{\b0\fs12}or your father, or your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.68,0:31:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想一次又一次陷入同樣的爭論之中\N{\b0\fs12}I will not get dragged into the same debate over and over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.01,0:31:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\b0\fs12}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.83,0:31:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,去找到西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Go get Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.75,0:31:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}Stop Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.59,0:31:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,做你該做的\N{\b0\fs12}Do whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.19,0:31:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,徹底解決問題\N{\b0\fs12}End this once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.25,0:32:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,停車  停車\N{\b0\fs12}Stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.22,0:33:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,萬聖節已經過去半年了  傻帽\N{\b0\fs12}Halloween was six months ago, ass hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.26,0:33:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,滾開  不然就放到你  聽到了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Now get off the road or get put down. You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.19,0:33:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我有個提議給你們\N{\b0\fs12}I have a proposal for you men.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.98,0:33:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-說  -奧利弗  你沒事吧\N{\b0\fs12}- Go! - Oliver, are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.73,0:33:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事  但西婭不在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, I'm fine, but Thea's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.56,0:33:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-你做到了  -做到什麼了\N{\b0\fs12}- You did it. - Did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.11,0:33:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭沒事  她沒事\N{\b0\fs12}Thea's fine. She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.49,0:34:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她五分鐘前走進了分局\N{\b0\fs12}She walked into the precinct five minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.34,0:34:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,安然無恙\N{\b0\fs12}Safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.44,0:34:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  你聽到了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver, did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.82,0:34:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-西婭呢  -她沒事  沒受傷\N{\b0\fs12}- Thea? - She's fine, no injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.57,0:34:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-他沒碰她  -他不在那裡\N{\b0\fs12}- He didn't touch her. - He wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.96,0:34:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-他手下很多雇傭兵  -他不在那裡\N{\b0\fs12}- He had a lot of men, hired guns. - He wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.92,0:34:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他正在別處忙活\N{\b0\fs12}Because he was busy elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.17,0:34:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,鐵山監獄重新啟用了一個地震中毀掉的區\N{\b0\fs12}Iron Heights reopened a wing damaged in the quake.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.28,0:34:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有一輛運囚車被斯萊德劫持了\N{\b0\fs12}There was a prisoner transfer. Slade hijacked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.39,0:34:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,為他的軍隊招募士兵\N{\b0\fs12}Soldiers for his army.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.72,0:34:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,綁架西婭只是為了分散注意力\N{\b0\fs12}Abducting Thea was all a diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.22,0:34:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.69,0:34:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,謝天謝地\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, thank god.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.64,0:34:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我的寶貝\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, my baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.78,0:34:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我的寶貝\N{\b0\fs12}Ohh! My baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.13,0:34:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.33,0:34:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他告訴我了\N{\b0\fs12}He told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.02,0:34:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,威爾遜先生\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Wilson...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.51,0:35:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他把你的秘密告訴我了\N{\b0\fs12}He told me your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.80,0:35:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這些年你是怎麼騙我的\N{\b0\fs12}How you've been lying to me for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.15,0:35:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎能不告訴我  馬爾科姆•梅林是我父親\N{\b0\fs12}How could you not tell me Malcolm Merlyn was my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.91,0:35:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我那麼信任你\N{\b0\fs12}I believed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.04,0:35:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是想保證你的安全\N{\b0\fs12}We were trying to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.84,0:35:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你這樣聽起來像誰嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you have any idea who you sound like?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.65,0:35:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,聽起來像她\N{\b0\fs12}You sound like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.26,0:35:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}Slade...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.67,0:35:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡太便宜他們了\N{\b0\fs12}Death's too good for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.23,0:35:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這個島就是對他們的懲罰\N{\b0\fs12}This island should be their punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.25,0:35:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡太便宜你們了\N{\b0\fs12}Death is too good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.50,0:35:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這個島就是對你們的懲罰\N{\b0\fs12}This island should be your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.71,0:35:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是他們餘生的牢籠\N{\b0\fs12}Their prison for the rest of their days.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.53,0:35:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是你們餘生的牢籠\N{\b0\fs12}Your prison for the rest of your days.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.08,0:36:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,帶他走\N{\b0\fs12}Get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.03,0:36:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}Slade...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.46,0:36:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,回去\N{\b0\fs12}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.92,0:36:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以幫你\N{\b0\fs12}I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.46,0:36:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是生  是死\N{\b0\fs12}You can live, or you can die.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.69,0:36:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己選\N{\b0\fs12}You choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.76,0:36:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你想給自己的家人捎點消息嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Would you like to send a message to your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.76,0:36:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,船修好之後我就去拜訪他們\N{\b0\fs12}'Cause as soon as this boat is fixed, I'm paying them a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.44,0:36:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}星城地界  您已出城
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.48,0:36:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,漫長的一夜啊\N{\b0\fs12}Hell of a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.75,0:36:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,昆汀•蘭斯  說話真委婉啊\N{\b0\fs12}Quentin Lance, master of the understatement.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.60,0:37:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,借一步說話  警官\N{\b0\fs12}A word, officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.57,0:37:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等  親愛的\N{\b0\fs12}Hold on, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.66,0:37:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.20,0:37:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經跟斯賓塞地檢官說過你的情況了\N{\b0\fs12}I've spoken to DA Spencer about your...situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.06,0:37:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她不想起訴...\N{\b0\fs12}She doesn't want to press charges--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.92,0:37:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,前提是你合作\N{\b0\fs12}if you cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.35,0:37:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我們治安維持者在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Tell us where the vigilante is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.94,0:37:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想告訴你們  可我不知道\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I'd love to, but I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.16,0:37:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那就太不幸了\N{\b0\fs12}Well, that's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.47,0:37:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,看樣子是的\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.05,0:37:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,昆汀•拉裡•蘭斯  你因為\N{\b0\fs12}Quentin Larry Lance, you're under arrest
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.47,0:37:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,參與謀劃幫助罪犯等多項罪名被捕\N{\b0\fs12}for conspiracy and aiding in multiple felonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.05,0:37:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什麼  你瘋了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}What? Are you out of your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.62,0:37:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼呢  威爾遜  是威爾遜幹的\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing? Wilson--Wilson did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.42,0:37:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我抓對人了  你...\N{\b0\fs12}I collared the right guy. What are you--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.14,0:37:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你有權保持沉默\N{\b0\fs12}You have the right to remain silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.26,0:37:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.48,0:37:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-你有權找律師協助  -爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}- You have the right to an attorney. - Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.83,0:37:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有專家稱這是大打同情牌\N{\b0\fs12}Riding what pundits are calling a sympathy bump,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.69,0:37:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是莫伊拉•奎恩在昨天\N{\b0\fs12}Moira Queen pulled far ahead of Sebastian Blood
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.45,0:37:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,剛進行的投票中  遠遠領先\N{\b0\fs12}in the latest polls conducted in
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.06,0:37:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安•布拉德...\N{\b0\fs12}the last 24 hours by channel--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.71,0:37:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然就這樣搞砸了\N{\b0\fs12}The whole thing just blew up in my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.67,0:37:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這讓我還怎麼當選\N{\b0\fs12}How the hell do I get elected now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.84,0:37:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是該換種語氣跟我說話\N{\b0\fs12}I think you intended a different tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.01,0:37:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你說過我會成為市長的\N{\b0\fs12}You said I'd be mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.63,0:38:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你就這樣把成果拱手讓給\N{\b0\fs12}And you just delivered this election
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.10,0:38:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,莫伊拉•奎恩了  為什麼\N{\b0\fs12}for Moira Queen, and for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.92,0:38:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟奎恩家族的人到底有什麼關係\N{\b0\fs12}What is this obsession you have with the Queen family?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.40,0:38:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒跟他說嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You haven't told him?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.37,0:38:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你答應過我的\N{\b0\fs12}You promised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.73,0:38:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過會把星城給你\N{\b0\fs12}I promised you this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.79,0:38:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我還說過給你一支軍隊讓你奪取星城\N{\b0\fs12}I promised you an army with which to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.14,0:38:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,現在什麼情況\N{\b0\fs12}What is our status?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.61,0:38:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,奎恩聯合企業的應用科學部門\N{\b0\fs12}Queen Consolidated's applied sciences division
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.97,0:38:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,正在全力\N{\b0\fs12}is now fully dedicated to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.56,0:38:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的血樣復制血清\N{\b0\fs12}replicating a serum based on your blood sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.48,0:38:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吧\N{\b0\fs12}You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.17,0:38:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一切皆在掌握之中\N{\b0\fs12}Everything is proceeding as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.23,0:38:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Where are you going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.76,0:38:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,去處理一下我的目標\N{\b0\fs12}To service my obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.80,0:38:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,得再讓奧利弗•奎恩分分神\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver Queen needs one more distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.58,0:39:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個在這裡幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.31,0:39:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們想著你會來這裡\N{\b0\fs12}We thought this is where you would go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.01,0:39:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這個不難猜  你最近一直\N{\b0\fs12}You're predictable. That, and you've been
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.27,0:39:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,都在這裡的小床上過夜\N{\b0\fs12}sleeping on the cot at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.49,0:39:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你們到底想幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.11,0:39:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要不我們去哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Where else would we be?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.59,0:39:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊是對的\N{\b0\fs12}Roy was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.93,0:39:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,每次轉折點上  我都會作出錯誤的決定\N{\b0\fs12}At every turn, I had made the wrong decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.80,0:39:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,對他\N{\b0\fs12}With him,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.71,0:39:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,對公司  還有...\N{\b0\fs12}with...the company, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.92,0:39:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,對西婭\N{\b0\fs12}and with Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.93,0:39:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我太專注於斯萊德對我的所作所為\N{\b0\fs12}I was so focused on what Slade might do to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.21,0:39:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,以至於我...\N{\b0\fs12}that it never...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.59,0:39:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,從沒想過自己會對自己作出什麼事\N{\b0\fs12}even occurred to me what I could do to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.44,0:40:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是自己最大的敵人\N{\b0\fs12}I am my own worst enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.73,0:40:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那是斯萊德說的  奧利弗  不要輕信他的話\N{\b0\fs12}That's Slade talking, Oliver. Don't let him in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.28,0:40:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他在我的腦海中揮之不去  狄格爾\N{\b0\fs12}I can't keep him out of my head, Diggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.33,0:40:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我...  我什麼事都阻止不了他\N{\b0\fs12}I can't...I can't stop him from doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.71,0:40:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以的\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.83,0:40:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你憑什麼這麼確定\N{\b0\fs12}What makes you so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.47,0:40:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因為有我們在\N{\b0\fs12}Because you're not alone, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.66,0:40:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,現在幹什麼  老大\N{\b0\fs12}Now what, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.72,0:40:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我們反擊\N{\b0\fs12}Now we fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.37,0:40:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,警方簽發了針對斯萊德•威爾遜的拘捕令\N{\b0\fs12}Police have issued a warrant for Slade Wilson
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.97,0:40:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因為西婭•奎恩指證\N{\b0\fs12}after Thea Queen named him
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.52,0:40:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他是綁架她的幕後黑手\N{\b0\fs12}as the mastermind of her kidnapping yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.22,0:40:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這是奎恩小姐被釋放  而威爾遜被捕\N{\b0\fs12}This in the wake of Wilson's arrest and subsequent release
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.52,0:40:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,然後又被星城警方釋放後幾個小時後的情況\N{\b0\fs12}by the SCPD hours before Ms. Queen was released.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.39,0:41:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在向媒體的聲明中\N{\b0\fs12}In a statement to the press,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.04,0:41:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,星城警署局長富蘭克林•派克\N{\b0\fs12}SCPD lieutenant Franklin Pike
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.18,0:41:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,重申了自己對警局方面的支持\N{\b0\fs12}reiterated his support for his department
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.64,0:41:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然這件事顯而易見是警方烏龍了\N{\b0\fs12}despite what appears to be a serious blunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.72,0:41:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他還說  星城警署有責任...\N{\b0\fs12}He went on to say, the SCPD is committed--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.62,0:41:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,確保對任何人的逮捕都符合法律規定\N{\b0\fs12}to making sure any arrest they make is a legal one,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.91,0:41:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是沒有充分證據...\N{\b0\fs12}but without sufficient--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.39,0:41:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不用害怕\N{\b0\fs12}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.15,0:41:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是來傷害你的\N{\b0\fs12}I am not here to harm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.14,0:41:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧\N{\b0\fs12}Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.53,0:41:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,人終有一死\N{\b0\fs12}All in good time, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.25,0:41:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我死前\N{\b0\fs12}But before then,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.25,0:41:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我要來星城\N{\b0\fs12}I have come to Starling City
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.61,0:41:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,看到奧利弗•奎恩痛苦\N{\b0\fs12}to see Oliver Queen suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.28,0:41:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗...  什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver...what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.50,0:41:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.36,0:41:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你根本不知道他的真面目\N{\b0\fs12}Because he's not the man you think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.99,0:41:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道\N{\b0\fs12}And how would you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.99,0:41:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我知道奧利弗•奎恩就是...\N{\b0\fs12}Because I know Oliver Queen is...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.11,0:41:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,綠箭俠\N{\b0\fs12}The Arrow.